38.6 pp reduction in OD (95% CI: &#x02212;14.2 to &#x02212;63.0 pp,
p = 0.002). There was a smaller reduction in OD in the villages in
the Volta region (&#x02212;12.4 pp, 95% CI: &#x02212;5.1 to &#x02212;19.7
pp, p = 0.001), and no statistically significant impact in the Central
region.</p><fig id="fig2" position="float"><label>Figure 2</label><caption><p>The full sample is 58 villages: 18 in Central, 20 in Upper West,
